verbose_text: HIF-1alpha expression also decreased in the ONC injured side in both the CP-MSC- and CB-MNC-transplanted groups at 4 weeks post-transplantation (p < 0.05; XREF_FIG) These findings suggest that transplantation procedures may induce HIF-1alpha expression, and the transplanted stem cells contribute to recovery of HIF-1alpha expression and possibly, neuronal survival in the injured optic nerve.
